ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"十一、Final揀位 瘋狂比人踢走 大大聲講無野話唔緊要 下一個shot即刻播海允比人踢完喊 成功營造天使image<br />\n十二、Final首歌降key唱 soyou仲要讚佢 明明降key其他人都唱到 AJY捧佢捧到出哂面<br />\n十三、最後排名公佈 上次18名升到第3名 扮驚訝 扮感動 但一滴眼淚都無 睇下同樣情況既安有真 金珉周同金彩元 反應差天共地 有d腦既都會睇得出<br />\n<br />\nIONE時期：<br />\n十四、Vlive 唔出聲無人理 唯一一次仲要係佢自己叫Sad Frog餵<br />\n十五、自九月一日起日日都有新面孔<br />\n十六、Nekkoya 練習片一個第三名嘅Vocal係Dance Break企C 仲要跳錯<br />\n十七、棒球賽公演 八婆撞我元英 Dance Break完就以為自己係C 唔係見到禾櫻轉去C位跳都唔知自己跳錯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icCnwNA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicCnwNA.gif&h=0f73af50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十八、唔知佢想點,hi醬生日v 成堆人攬埋一夠得佢企左邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4RDjeG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4RDjeG.gif&h=a939c476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十九、hi醬生日v 佢拎牙咬嘢仲要周圍吐,仲要一野撞走禾真,嗰粒嘢嚇到禾真之外,佢仲lur咗落啲匙羹到 btw佢推個膊頭出黎嗰下好似楊怡gif<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/8L0OAwcmkyg6mEDde2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F8L0OAwcmkyg6mEDde2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=bda92012&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/jaHSDHo3BKfWJplBdB/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FjaHSDHo3BKfWJplBdB%2Fgiphy.gif&h=e13c9628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十、La Vie en Rose初一位唔so偶校既人。發夠centre夢未啊！屌推夠真真走未啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/213704_8f8dcff3aed61cbd841b2c859f625710.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F213704_8f8dcff3aed61cbd841b2c859f625710.gif&h=9300a203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十一、ENOZI Cam第二集 係nako仁美隔離打乞嚏仲唔捂口 有無衛生常識嫁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/12/204808_9bc9b64b1c238af2bb6d1d6a41708366.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F12%2F204808_9bc9b64b1c238af2bb6d1d6a41708366.gif&h=147c7ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十二、The Show下班訪問，其他人都擺緊首歌嘅開場pose，唯獨佢無啦啦發centre夢係後面行去中間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEcPUW5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEcPUW5.gif&h=78d992f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十三、QT Show咁多鏡頭影住都撩牙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nM3vGuO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnM3vGuO.gif&h=c24428aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十四、meet and greet 成班係塊透明牌度簽名 條八婆第2個簽 簽係中間右小小仲要勁大 塊牌咁細要簽12個名 仲要簽到咁大係咪玩野? 簽個名又要c?<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/19/CP0MJd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2FCP0MJd.png&h=24a34aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞到彩讌都唔知簽邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/fwZE1DvyEgi7ROfQXm/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FfwZE1DvyEgi7ROfQXm%2Fgiphy.gif&h=cee861e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十五、開V講返La Vie En Rose活動最後一次FS啲野 到個八婆講野時 佢噤停全部人 要全部人留心聽佢講嘢 好大個官威<br />\n（詳：<a href=\"https://www.vlive.tv/video/99713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vlive.tv%2Fvideo%2F99713&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=fea7a7b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vlive.tv/video/99713</a> 6:12)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxNETYu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuxNETYu.png&h=52eb51af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十六、偶像運動會當眾撩鼻<br />\n(以下照片可能令人情緒不安：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/PL8HLUr.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL8HLUr.gif&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c8e6866b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/PL8HLUr.gif</a>)<br />\n二十七、SMA 妹妹line收工，個個走曬得油b仲係度，結果要3個成員返去接佢，好大個官威  (妹妹line走個時冇人在意過仲有油狗呢個人)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UYXy9q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2UYXy9q.gif&h=e9ea24c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h38kwV9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh38kwV9.gif&h=d7d49aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十八、櫻係mail講佢成日係宿舍唱歌同播歌，歌聲環繞住成個宿舍，仁美大師就直接d，係節目爆佢朝早會好大聲聽歌嘈住人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRx8Om0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRx8Om0.png&h=0f31b64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二十九、蛙蛙係mail講佢係咁叫油b唔好講鬼故，但油b仲專登講黎嚇佢<br />\n三十、吃放vlive，油狗冇問過人就撈晒d料入牛肉度，睇下小天使個無奈樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S218Za5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS218Za5.gif&h=35058dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三十一、奈子生日V，娜B爆料，個八婆每日都蝦奈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7gXm0i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7gXm0i.jpg&h=2fe5fc8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牙純既快人快語 一言道破<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qye8Fj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qye8Fj.jpg&h=96edd040&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b18361ed90d28fe76da1ec8f1f39e0b21e96774","tid":1439653,"uid":61679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">本討論區是韓國Mnet在2018年推出的選拔實境節目《Produce 48》撚鳩參加者同觀眾後，而推出的屌柒區</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/151823_79dc4aa3b328f0c499b67adf13e2f339.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F151823_79dc4aa3b328f0c499b67adf13e2f339.png&h=e6d37a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">食屎啦mnet</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/151847_538b7f48334279f57f48b5d36944bb0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice